data.description: Charming home in Houndslake's Bungalow Village! This bungalow is tucked away for privacy on a wooded lot but conveniently located near the Houndslake Country Club, shopping, and restaurants. Sit on the front porch with your coffee and enjoy the beautiful landscape in the morning and entertain on the back deck in the evenings.  The open floor plan features a great room with vaulted ceiling and a gas fireplace. Eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances and island. Primary bedroom has large closet. Refrigerator, washer and dryer stay! Dining room can also be used as an office, ample storage under the house, security sysytem, sprinkler system, koi pond, and much more.  Home is being sold ''As-Is''.  Schedule your showing today!
